snippet.title: Official Reveal Trailer | Call of Duty: Black Ops 2
snippet.description:
Black Ops is back. Experience near-future black operations with the next evolution of the legendary Call of Duty: Black Ops. 

Pre-order now http://www.callofduty.com/blackops2. #BlackOps2 coming 11.13.12.
